# ============================================
# DOCUMENTATION
# ============================================
# Keep main project docs, ignore temporary/summary docs
!README.md
!SETUP.md
!CONTRIBUTING.md
!CHANGELOG.md
!LICENSE
!docs/
!documentation/

# Ignore temporary/summary documentation files
*_SUMMARY.md
*_COMPLETE.md
UPDATES_*.md
DEPLOYMENT.md
DATABASE_CONFIG.md
SETUP_DEPLOYMENT.md
CONFIGURATION_COMPLETE.md
TESTING_COMPLETE.md
FINAL_TESTING_SUMMARY.md
SECURITY_*.md
